1. clickhouse-client --chime 1, slow query, redirected stderr: no BEL
2. clickhouse-client --chime 10, fast query: no BEL
3. clickhouse-client (no --chime), 1.5s < default 5s threshold: no BEL
4. clickhouse-client --chime 1, slow query then error, redirected stderr: no BEL
5. clickhouse-local --chime 1, slow query, redirected stderr: no BEL
6. clickhouse-client --chime 0, slow query: no BEL
7. clickhouse-client --chime 1, slow query, pty stderr: BEL
8. clickhouse-client --chime 0, slow query (~6s > default 5s threshold), pty stderr: no BEL
9. clickhouse-client --chime 10, fast query (0.1s < 10s threshold), pty stderr: no BEL
10. clickhouse-client (no --chime), slow query (~6s > default 5s threshold), pty stderr: BEL
11. clickhouse-client --chime 1, slow query then error, pty stderr: BEL
12. clickhouse-client --chime (implicit value), slow query (~6s > default 5s threshold), pty stderr: BEL
